Yeah, well...

893
00:40:32,960 --> 00:40:36,340
These days girls have wedding demands.

894
00:40:37,230 --> 00:40:39,420
But shouldn't we keep it reasonable?

895
00:40:40,070 --> 00:40:41,980
This house is too expensive.

896
00:40:42,000 --> 00:40:43,570
When I married your sister-in-law,

897
00:40:43,800 --> 00:40:44,860
