898
00:40:45,110 --> 00:40:45,980
And we've been doing fine

899
00:40:46,000 --> 00:40:46,740
for the past ten years.

900
00:40:46,760 --> 00:40:47,210
Wait a second.

901
00:40:47,320 --> 00:40:48,090
What do you mean?

902
00:40:49,840 --> 00:40:50,940
Do you think

903
00:40:50,960 --> 00:40:52,650
I asked for this house?

904
00:40:53,550 --> 00:40:54,210
Didn't you?

905
00:40:55,710 --> 00:40:57,300
