907
00:41:01,110 --> 00:41:02,530
I'm just trying to
understand the situation.

908
00:41:02,550 --> 00:41:04,420
I just wanted to know what's going on.

909
00:41:04,630 --> 00:41:05,740
Keep your voice down.

910
00:41:06,000 --> 00:41:06,780
The kid just fell asleep.

911
00:41:07,480 --> 00:41:08,210
What's wrong with you two?

912
00:41:09,510 --> 00:41:10,170
What's wrong?

913
00:41:11,150 --> 00:41:12,530
Just trying to understand the situation.

914
00:41:12,800 --> 00:41:13,940
Your husband is criticizing me.

915
00:41:14,280 --> 00:41:15,900
No, that's not what I meant.

916
00:41:16,030 --> 00:41:17,300
Do you know what today is?

917
00:41:17,510 --> 00:41:18,650
Why can't you say something nice?

918
00:41:18,880 --> 00:41:19,860
I didn't say anything.

919
00:41:20,110 --> 00:41:20,900
Didn't you?

920
00:41:21,230 --> 00:41:22,420
Didn't you say I was materialistic?

921
00:41:22,920 --> 00:41:24,050
When did I say that?

922
00:41:24,070 --> 00:41:25,460
That's what you meant.

923
00:41:26,280 --> 00:41:28,260
Tell me, I'll have your back.

924
00:41:29,030 --> 00:41:30,650
I know you mean well to me.

925
00:41:31,590 --> 00:41:32,530
Zijian and I

