931
00:41:43,960 --> 00:41:45,460
But Zijian is good to me.

932
00:41:45,840 --> 00:41:47,530
He wants to give me a better life.

933
00:41:48,320 --> 00:41:49,940
Besides, we didn't actually
buy this house.

934
00:41:50,800 --> 00:41:53,490
It was a gift from Long
as an employee benefit.

935
00:41:53,960 --> 00:41:54,940
A gift?

936
00:41:57,960 --> 00:41:58,740
You didn't pay?

937
00:41:59,400 --> 00:41:59,780
No.

938
00:42:08,840 --> 00:42:09,260
Long.

939
00:42:17,110 --> 00:42:19,210
Zijian has done a lot for Long

940
00:42:19,840 --> 00:42:21,130
over the years at Tianlong Group,

941
00:42:21,480 --> 00:42:22,570
recovering a bunch of debts.

942
00:42:23,550 --> 00:42:25,420
Now he's a golden boy in Tianlong Group.

943
00:42:26,030 --> 00:42:28,460
Besides, this whole complex
is owned by Tianlong Group.

944
00:42:28,670 --> 00:42:30,170
So, of course we get first dibs.

945
00:42:31,550 --> 00:42:34,050
It kinda makes sense.

946
00:42:37,360 --> 00:42:38,900
And I heard that this property

947
00:42:39,150 --> 00:42:41,130
is the hottest in Dongping right now.

948
00:42:41,440 --> 00:42:42,340
People are scrambling to buy in.

949
00:42:43,110 --> 00:42:45,530
As her brother, you should be
happy for her.

950
00:42:46,880 --> 00:42:48,980
Besides, with such a big place,

951
00:42:49,480 --> 00:42:51,380
you and Zijian can have a bunch of kids

952
00:42:51,400 --> 00:42:52,260
to fill the rooms.

953
00:42:52,760 --> 00:42:53,170
Oh, right,

954
00:42:53,360 --> 00:42:54,940
Qiqi's starting middle school soon, right?

955
00:42:55,400 --> 00:42:57,860
The best school in the city
is right outside the gate.

956
00:42:58,000 --> 00:42:58,460
Then,

957
00:42:58,590 --> 00:43:00,460
you can move Qiqi's
household registration here.

958
00:43:00,590 --> 00:43:02,900
Don't worry, Zijian won't say no.

959
00:43:04,320 --> 00:43:04,690
Am I right?

960
00:43:05,880 --> 00:43:06,380
Yanxin.

961
00:43:07,710 --> 00:43:08,420
Long.

962
00:43:09,070 --> 00:43:11,010
Long, welcome.

963
00:43:11,280 --> 00:43:12,210
Happy for you guys.

964
00:43:12,230 --> 00:43:12,740
Thank you.

965
00:43:12,760 --> 00:43:14,130
Sorry, I'm late.

966
00:43:14,320 --> 00:43:14,900
We rushed over here.

967
00:43:15,320 --> 00:43:17,170
Chen Shenglong, CEO of Tianlong Group.

968
00:43:17,760 --> 00:43:18,820
This is my brother-in-law, Li Renjun.

969
00:43:19,510 --> 00:43:19,900
Mr. Li.

970
00:43:20,630 --> 00:43:21,260
I heard a lot about you.

971
00:43:21,800 --> 00:43:22,260
Nice to meet you.

972
00:43:22,510 --> 00:43:23,740
This is my sister-in-law, Liu Yun.

973
00:43:23,960 --> 00:43:24,380
Director Liu.

974
00:43:25,280 --> 00:43:26,050
We finally met.

975
00:43:26,550 --> 00:43:26,940
Hello.

976
00:43:27,670 --> 00:43:28,130
You,

977
00:43:29,190 --> 00:43:30,170
beautiful bride.

978
00:43:30,590 --> 00:43:31,210
Take this red envelope.

979
00:43:31,880 --> 00:43:32,740
-Thank you, Long.
- Li Yanxin.

980
00:43:33,000 --> 00:43:33,860
He already gave you

981
00:43:33,880 --> 00:43:35,260
